rows.label: tlk70000043_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Yikes... There were about a hundred
times that I thought I was a goner!!!

rows.label: tlk70000043_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Just thinking about it chills my bones!
The capital could have been completely
destroyed in the attack!

rows.label: tlk70000043_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm glad that the legendary Iiran
cooking didn't get wiped from the
history books for good!

rows.label: tlk70000043_02_msg0004
rows.name:
That wouldnae make me happy!
The maturity and subtleness of Iiran
cuisine needs handing down the ages!

rows.label: tlk70000043_02_msg0005
rows.name:
I'll do whatever I can to make tha'
happen.

rows.label: tlk70000043_02_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm only one man, but as a food
researcher, I'll carry on fighting to
the bitter end!
